WEBVTT

00:00:00.599 --> 00:00:03.070
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:05.269
I just want to say thank you all. God

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:06.829
bless every single one of you. Thank you

00:00:06.839 --> 00:00:09.150
for coming on here and praying with me

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:12.629
every day; it's such a blessing. I've

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:14.110
been seeking the Lord

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:15.990
with all my heart the last couple of days,

00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:21.670
just looking for that fresh touch.

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:24.470
So many people are

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:27.910
desperate for a fresh touch from Jesus. The

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:27.920
Lord has

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.990
been dealing

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.549
with

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:33.750
me about

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:35.310
prophetic voices and people in

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:37.229
big

00:00:37.239 --> 00:00:42.709
ministries. I was caught in the

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:45.709
spirit and saw many ministers,

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.790
and the Lord said, 'Brandon, they

00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:53.630
don't know what's

00:00:53.630 --> 00:00:53.640
coming.'A

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:55.990
lot of them don't know

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.709
because they've

00:00:58.719 --> 00:01:03.869
allowed the pressure from the

00:01:03.879 --> 00:01:07.350
people and the pride of life to clog

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:10.550
their spiritual ears. You're not able

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:13.630
to hear—or you’re

00:01:13.630 --> 00:01:13.640
hearing only partially—something

00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:15.630
very vital for what's

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:18.190
coming, but you're not hearing

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:21.310
the depth of

00:01:21.310 --> 00:01:21.320
it.

00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:23.789
Then He showed me the

00:01:23.799 --> 00:01:25.550
people who say, 'Well, we're always

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:27.390
going to pray away things; we're always

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:30.469
going to stop

00:01:30.469 --> 00:01:30.479
things.'He

00:01:30.479 --> 00:01:31.789
was showing me that there are

00:01:31.799 --> 00:01:33.069
some things that are not going to be

00:01:33.079 --> 00:01:35.270
stopped,

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:38.510
and yet it will

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:42.030
catch a lot of you off

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:45.910
guard because you're not hearing

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:49.069
Him. Because

00:01:49.069 --> 00:01:49.079
of

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:52.109
the fear of what you think is coming, you

00:01:52.119 --> 00:01:54.709
put the wall up, and God is saying,

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:56.510
'Warning, warning,

00:01:56.510 --> 00:01:56.520
warning.'There's

00:01:56.520 --> 00:01:58.149
a road out ahead, but

00:01:58.159 --> 00:01:59.590
you say, 'No, I'm going to pray against the

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:02.670
road being out; I'm going to stop the road from

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:07.029
being out with my prayer.'But the road is

00:02:07.039 --> 00:02:09.229
out, and you're going to keep driving

00:02:09.239 --> 00:02:10.869
that way because you think you're going

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:13.110
to pray against the road that's out and

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.470
change it, when God is just telling you

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:17.550
to pause for a minute,

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:20.309
listen to a new plan, and take time to

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:22.949
get out of the car and climb. Does that

00:02:22.959 --> 00:02:25.589
make

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:28.190
sense? The Lord was showing me a lot

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:30.430
of prophetic voices that started

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:31.910
out

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:34.750
pure,

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:37.350
but

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:39.149
the more

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:40.830
they got into ministry and the more the

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:42.949
pressure and opinions

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:46.070
of people came, they

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:48.589
didn't filter it right. They didn't keep

00:02:48.599 --> 00:02:51.270
vertical, and because of this, they became

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:54.190
a mixture.

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:56.750
The more the mixture of the world

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:58.509
comes in, you've got the Holy Spirit,

00:02:58.509 --> 00:02:58.519
but

00:02:58.519 --> 00:02:59.910
you're mixing it

00:02:59.910 --> 00:02:59.920
together.

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:01.670
Instead of keeping

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:06.309
Him first, ego sets in, and

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:08.869
you think, 'I'm going to run

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:11.509
this ministry; I'm going to do this the

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:14.149
way that I think I

00:03:14.149 --> 00:03:14.159
should,'listening

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:16.350
to Him partially. You've got

00:03:16.350 --> 00:03:16.360
one

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:18.509
ear over here, but

00:03:18.519 --> 00:03:21.030
you don't have both ears to

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:24.110
Him. I saw them getting a message

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:26.630
from the Father, but it was only at a

00:03:26.630 --> 00:03:26.640
certain

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:30.190
level. He showed me that

00:03:30.190 --> 00:03:30.200
as ministries

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:33.110
got bigger,

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:40.670
their reception

00:03:40.670 --> 00:03:40.680
antenna

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:45.350
started to become out

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:45.360
of

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:48.110
tune. He said, 'They're not hearing Me

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.110
in the higher

00:03:51.519 --> 00:03:54.789
levels in the throne room; they're

00:03:54.799 --> 00:03:57.229
picking it up down here, but they're not

00:03:57.239 --> 00:03:59.990
hearing Me in the throne

00:03:59.990 --> 00:04:00.000
room.'If

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.789
you stop hearing Me in the throne room,

00:04:02.799 --> 00:04:04.470
you're going to

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:05.589
get

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:08.190
off-track;

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:10.110
you're not getting the whole picture.

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:11.830
It's like being a Watchman

00:04:11.830 --> 00:04:11.840
on the wall;

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:14.030
you see

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:16.789
the horizon,

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:20.430
but you have blinders on.

00:04:20.440 --> 00:04:21.590
You're not able to see the whole

00:04:21.590 --> 00:04:21.600
landscape

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:22.909
because you have patches on your eyes

00:04:22.919 --> 00:04:25.110
like a horse.

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:29.990
You need to look

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.189
at the whole landscape of what He's

00:04:31.199 --> 00:04:32.749
saying prophetically, but they're only

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:34.150
getting a little bit because

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:38.189
they've got all this stuff going on

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:42.150
and they're not staying vertical with

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.469
Him. The Lord said to me,

00:04:44.479 --> 00:04:47.390
'Brandon, there are great dark

00:04:47.400 --> 00:04:51.430
things coming, but many of My people,

00:04:51.440 --> 00:04:53.390
because there's a mixture, I'm not able

00:04:53.400 --> 00:04:55.510
to get the pure thing through them

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:58.430
anymore to warn My people for what's

00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:03.150
coming. You must stay vertical

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:08.270
with Me and don't allow any mixture

00:05:08.270 --> 00:05:08.280
in.'He

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:11.990
said this is vital. He said, 'I will

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:14.909
not do anything in this world unless I

00:05:14.919 --> 00:05:17.270
reveal it to My prophets first,'but

00:05:17.270 --> 00:05:17.280
He

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:20.029
can only reveal it

00:05:20.039 --> 00:05:22.270
to the ones who are

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:25.590
vertical, keeping their eyes on Him and not

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:29.990
allowing fame and ego to get in the way.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:32.150
When you start thinking

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:34.309
it's

00:05:34.309 --> 00:05:34.319
you—the

00:05:34.319 --> 00:05:38.110
glove instead of the hand in the

00:05:38.110 --> 00:05:38.120
glove—He's

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:40.390
not able to use you like He was

00:05:40.390 --> 00:05:40.400
before

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:43.510
because the glove gets in the

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:46.189
way. You've got to keep yourself and

00:05:46.189 --> 00:05:46.199
your

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:49.309
ego out of the way. I saw many

00:05:49.319 --> 00:05:53.230
ministers who, as they got famous,

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:11.230
became

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:14.070
horizontal, looking at everybody else's

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:14.080
praise, and

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:16.670
stopped looking vertical. The

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:19.430
Lord told me, 'There are many of My

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:22.870
ministers that started out right,

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:22.880
Brandon.'They

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:25.270
started out with

00:06:25.270 --> 00:06:25.280
a

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:29.070
pure heart

00:06:29.070 --> 00:06:29.080
before

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:30.670
the Father,

00:06:30.670 --> 00:06:30.680
but

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:32.749
you're going to

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:34.950
see a house of cards fall with a lot of

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:35.830
these ministries. You're going to see a

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:38.150
cleaning of the house in 2025 and

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:38.160
2026—a

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:41.189
great

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:43.230
uncovering of

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:47.990
darkness.

00:06:55.759 --> 00:06:58.550
It's vital for you ministers

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:03.270
to always keep Jesus

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:06.309
first and deflate your ego. It grieved me

00:07:06.309 --> 00:07:06.319
when

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:08.990
He said to me

00:07:11.879 --> 00:07:14.150
that

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:20.430
Saul

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:24.309
started out good,

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.110
but he let a mixture

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:34.869
in until the

00:07:34.869 --> 00:07:34.879
anointing departed from

00:07:34.879 --> 00:07:37.830
him.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:42.550
He wanted the prophet

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:44.230
to walk with him so they could

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:47.110
pretend he still had it,

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:49.189
but

00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:51.309
the anointing that

00:07:51.319 --> 00:07:55.149
was on his life had already left

00:07:55.159 --> 00:07:57.550
and gone to David.

00:07:57.560 --> 00:08:00.189
I told

00:08:00.199 --> 00:08:01.830
you the Davids are

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:04.550
coming

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:07.309
because the

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:10.670
Sauls have lost the anointing.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:20.430
I saw so many of them

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:22.230
behind the pulpit

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:24.350
hearing a little bit, but

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:26.390
it wasn't the whole message.

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:29.309
Because of ego,

00:08:29.319 --> 00:08:31.390
fame, and money,

00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:33.709
they lost themselves in

00:08:33.709 --> 00:08:33.719
it and

00:08:33.719 --> 00:08:38.550
forgot to stay

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:40.909
vertical. We pray for every one of

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:43.430
them; we're not better than

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:48.070
any of

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:50.509
them, but there's a great

00:08:50.519 --> 00:08:52.310
shaking coming.

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:55.750
I don't want to ever

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:57.069
allow a

00:08:57.079 --> 00:09:00.509
platform to destroy my relationship

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:01.790
with my

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:04.230
Father;

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:09.990
it's the most important thing to

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:14.110
me. All this other stuff is just crap, quite

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:17.230
frankly.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:20.670
It's about Him and me staying

00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:24.110
pliable and allowing the glove to be

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:26.230
there for that hand, the Holy Spirit, to

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:28.110
flow.

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:31.110
As long as I keep my eyes on

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:35.670
Him

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:35.680
and

00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:39.750
deflect the glory and praise

00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:41.990
to the Father, I am just a

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:44.590
vessel.

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.870
Deflect the glory like

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:05.910
a mirror;

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:08.269
when the light shines on it,

00:10:08.279 --> 00:10:09.470
you

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:12.550
just deflect it right to the Father.

00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:19.590
Ego stays out of the way

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.910
because you're just like the donkey;

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:24.389
he could have gotten arrogant because

00:10:24.389 --> 00:10:24.399
everyone

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:25.670
was

00:10:28.839 --> 00:10:30.829
laying palm leaves at

00:10:30.829 --> 00:10:30.839
his

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:32.910
feet, but

00:10:32.910 --> 00:10:32.920
it had

00:10:32.920 --> 00:10:34.670
nothing to

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:36.069
do with him; it had everything to do with

00:10:36.079 --> 00:10:43.430
the One riding on his

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.829
back.

00:10:46.839 --> 00:10:50.509
I'm desperate for more of

00:10:50.519 --> 00:10:53.389
Him. A lot of people

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:56.230
don't get me,

00:10:56.230 --> 00:10:56.240
and

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:58.150
big ministers reject me,

00:11:03.710 --> 00:11:03.720
but

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.790
I don't care. It's not

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:14.470
about me; it's about

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:17.670
Jesus.

00:11:24.920 --> 00:11:27.550
I just want

00:11:27.560 --> 00:11:29.629
Him to say, 'Well done, thou good and

00:11:29.639 --> 00:11:30.750
faithful

00:11:33.910 --> 00:11:33.920
servant.'My

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:39.910
job is to warn you,

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:58.870
shouting it from the wall as loud

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:02.710
as I can. Jesus is coming

00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:04.790
soon.

00:12:04.800 --> 00:12:09.030
No man

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:12.310
knows the day or the hour,

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:14.990
but

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:17.389
He said

00:12:20.710 --> 00:12:20.720
to

00:12:24.399 --> 00:12:27.509
tell My people

00:12:30.399 --> 00:12:33.110
that time is running out.

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:41.990
The Ark door is about to close, and

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:44.189
many are going to

00:12:44.199 --> 00:12:45.269
be left

00:12:45.279 --> 00:12:48.710
behind.

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:53.230
You must help me bring in My

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:57.030
harvest. In these times of staying

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:59.470
vertical,

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:02.629
He

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:05.710
said, 'Brandon, there's mixture today; I need you

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:08.509
to separate yourself even

00:13:08.519 --> 00:13:10.790
more.'I

00:13:12.430 --> 00:13:12.440
get

00:13:14.509 --> 00:13:14.519
distracted

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:19.189
with

00:13:25.399 --> 00:13:27.750
people pulling, but He said

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.710
a greater wave is coming

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:29.720
and I’m

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:31.750
acclimating right now.

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:34.389
Let's go higher. It's time to go

00:13:34.399 --> 00:13:41.870
higher.

00:13:41.880 --> 00:13:44.150
Ladies and gentlemen,

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:45.750
He wants to use

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:45.760
you

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:48.310
too.

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:52.110
Will you be that vessel?

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:55.110
Will you allow the Holy Spirit to

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:58.590
flow through you and not be a dam to

00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:00.790
reach the ones I would never have

00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:03.949
the opportunity to speak to?

00:14:03.959 --> 00:14:05.670
Your family

00:14:05.670 --> 00:14:05.680
might

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:08.710
never turn on my YouTube channel,

00:14:08.710 --> 00:14:08.720
but

00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:11.389
they'll

00:14:11.399 --> 00:14:14.629
listen to

00:14:14.639 --> 00:14:18.670
you. Be bold in this hour,

00:14:21.509 --> 00:14:21.519
letting

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:27.269
your

00:14:27.279 --> 00:14:29.870
voice be the one crying in

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:32.350
the darkness.

00:14:46.959 --> 00:14:48.749
The Lord told

00:14:48.749 --> 00:14:48.759
me that

00:14:48.759 --> 00:14:51.310
the window for preaching the gospel freely on the

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:55.110
internet

00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:59.509
is coming to a close soon.

00:14:59.519 --> 00:15:01.670
When the door

00:15:01.680 --> 00:15:04.509
closes, it will be closed forever.

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:13.509
I don't

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:17.110
know

00:15:18.949 --> 00:15:18.959
if

00:15:21.880 --> 00:15:23.629
it's four or five years,

00:15:23.639 --> 00:15:25.870
but He said

00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:28.430
this window of

00:15:28.430 --> 00:15:28.440
freedom

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:30.430
of speech will

00:15:30.430 --> 00:15:30.440
come to

00:15:30.440 --> 00:15:32.509
an abrupt

00:15:32.509 --> 00:15:32.519
end.

00:15:32.519 --> 00:15:34.590
Right

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:37.710
now,

00:15:41.030 --> 00:15:41.040
we

00:15:44.319 --> 00:15:47.550
have an opportunity to spread

00:15:47.550 --> 00:15:47.560
the

00:15:47.560 --> 00:15:50.990
gospel throughout the whole world. Some

00:15:50.990 --> 00:15:51.000
nations

